This turbulence module makes use of the FFTW3 library (www.fftw.org).

To install:
wget http://www.fftw.org/fftw-3.3.8.tar.gz
tar -xf fftw-3.3.8.tar.gz
cd fftw-3.3.8/
./configure --prefix=$HOME/local/
make
make install

If you use a different path for configure, you need to adjust the library path in the makefile.